theorem P3_prod_univ {X Y : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] [TopologicalSpace Y]
    {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P3 (A ×ˢ (Set.univ : Set Y)) ↔ Topology.P3 A := by
  have hUnivNonempty : (Set.univ : Set Y).Nonempty := Set.nonempty_univ
  constructor
  · intro hProd
    -- Extract `P3` for the first factor using the existing projection lemma.
    exact
      Topology.P3_of_P3_prod_left
        (A := A) (B := (Set.univ : Set Y)) hUnivNonempty hProd
  · intro hA
    -- Combine with `P3` for `Set.univ` to obtain `P3` for the product.
    exact
      Topology.P3_prod
        hA (Topology.P3_univ (X := Y))

theorem Set.nonempty_univ {α : Type*} [Nonempty α] :
    (Set.univ : Set α).Nonempty := by
  classical
  rcases ‹Nonempty α› with ⟨a⟩
  exact ⟨a, by simp⟩
